high_descs: Turn around and head to the table.
Pick up the knife in front of the tomato.
Cut the tomato in front of the pot on the table.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn around and go back to the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn to the right and go to the microwave.
Put the slice of tomato in the microwave, cook it, and pick it back up.
Go back to the sink.
Put the slice of tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Slice the tomato on the table
Turn right and go to the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Turn around, go to the table, turn right
Pick up a tomato slice from the table
Turn right and go to the sink, turn left to the microwave
Put the tomato slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the tomato slice from the microwave
Go to the front of the sink
Put the tomato in the sink
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato, cook a slice of it

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table with tomatoes on it.
Pick up the knife under the tomato on the right.
Cut the tomato on the right into slices.
Take the knife and walk to the sink to your right.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around and walk back to the table with the sliced tomato on it.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Take the tomato slice to the microwave to your right.
Open door and place slice inside, and then close door the turn on for four seconds, and then remove tomato slice.
Close microwave door and carry slice to the sink to your right.
Place the tomato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved piece of tomato in the sink.
